<item>
            <title>[SOLR-8799] Improve error message when tuple can&apos;t be read by SolrJ JDBC</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-8799</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the error message prints &quot;Can&apos;t read first tuple&quot; with the full stack trace having the full error. This isn&apos;t useful for JDBC clients since they don&apos;t show the full stack trace.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
